text: Sara Maliqi (born 9 October 1995) is an Albanian footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Albania women's national team. ==Career== Maliqi has been capped for the Albania national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Albanian women's footballers Category:Albania women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders Category:KFF Vllaznia Shkodër players
